</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Po inštalácii skontrolujte geometriu predných kolies. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
